OL,3,CSaltburn's iconic cliff lift to reopen
OL,4,Cfollowing fire
OL,6,FThe Saltburn Cliff Tramway will reopen
OL,7,Fthis week following a fire which
OL,8,Frequired the attraction to undergo an
OL,9,Fextensive restoration.
OL,11,FOpening on Friday (27 September), a
OL,12,Fdecision has been taken to keep the
OL,13,Ficonic cliff lift open daily until
OL,14,FJanuary for a longer period than usual.
OL,16,FThe tramway has been closed since
OL,17,FJanuary when an electrical fire
OL,18,Fstarted in the Grade-II listed pump
OL,19,Froom and caused extensive damage.
