OL,3,CSaltburn's iconic cliff lift to reopen
OL,4,Cfollowing fire
OL,6,FA full rewire and replacement of
OL,7,Fbespoke equipment was needed as well
OL,8,Fas improvements to the control system.
OL,9,FA full maintenance programme has also
OL,10,Ftaken place.
OL,12,FThe two cars remained undamaged due to
OL,13,Fthem being positioned halfway along
OL,14,Fthe track for the off season.
OL,16,FDue to the structure's historical
OL,17,Fimportance, special permission had to
OL,18,Fbe granted for work to take place.
