OL,3,CSaltburn's iconic cliff lift to reopen
OL,4,Cfollowing fire
OL,6,FCllr Carrie Richardson, cabinet member
OL,7,Ffor climate and culture and deputy
OL,8,Fleader, said: "The word 'iconic' can
OL,9,Fbe overused but it is absolutely the
OL,10,Fright word for the Saltburn Tramway.
OL,12,F"It is famous across the country and
OL,13,Fhas been much loved right here in the
OL,14,FTees Valley for many generations ` so
OL,15,Fit's wonderful to see it back to all
OL,16,Fits glory once again.
