OL,6,FThe damage done to the structure
OL,7,Frequired a long restoration which
OL,8,Fmeant even though a full electrical
OL,9,Frewire and new glazing installed in
OL,10,FMay, work had to continue over the
OL,11,Fpeak summer months.
OL,13,FCllr Carrie Richardson added: "It has
OL,14,Fbeen frustrating that the work took a
OL,15,Flong time, especially in the summer
OL,16,Fmonths.
OL,18,F"However, our visitors have understood
OL,19,Fthat it had to be carefully restored
OL,20,Fand it needed specialist work done
OL,21,Fthoroughly.
