OL,3,CSaltburn's iconic cliff lift to reopen
OL,4,Cfollowing fire
OL,6,F"We also took the opportunity to
OL,7,Fundertake a full maintenance programme
OL,8,Fand we are keeping it open for longer
OL,9,Fhours every day until January."
OL,11,FThe Tramway will operate most days
OL,12,Ffrom 10.30am on Friday 27 September
OL,13,Funtil 31 October 2024, daily 10.30am
OL,14,Fto 5pm.
OL,16,FAnd from 1 November 2024 to 5 January
OL,17,F2025 it will be open daily from
OL,18,F10.30am to 4pm.
